# Headless dispatch mode. One of:
#   off    — real headful (requires DISPLAY / WAYLAND_DISPLAY or xvfb-run)
#   new    — modern Chromium --headless=new (server default)
#   legacy — old --headless (don't pick this; documented for parity only)
# Unset → mochi auto-picks: "new" on Linux + no DISPLAY, "off" elsewhere.
MOCHI_HEADLESS=
